  "original_title": "\u0ba8\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0b95\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bca\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8 \u0bae\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b89\u0ba4\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bcb\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0b85\u0bae\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95 \u0b87\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9c\u0bbe\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95 \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bb2\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bb0\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Let's help the people of Sri Lanka in crisis - US Secretary of State",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "A meeting between the Sri Lankan Ambassador to the US, Mahinda Samarasinghe, and Secretary of the US Department of State, Anne J. Blinken, took place two weeks ago, during which Anne Blinken reaffirmed her commitment to help the people of Sri Lanka, who are facing a massive crisis.",
        "Now that the country is facing a massive economic crisis, the United States has been providing aid to India in recent times, and high-level meetings with the United States have also taken place.",
        "In particular, the Sri Lankan ambassador to the United States, Mahinda Samarasinghe, had met the American President Joe Biden a few weeks ago and briefed him on the current situation in the country.",
        "In conjunction with that, a meeting with the US Secretary of State, Henry J.",
        "Meanwhile, a group consisting of high-level representatives of the US Department of State and the US Treasury visited Sri Lanka last week and held discussions with various parties regarding the country's economic situation and the assistance needed to recover from this crisis.",
        "In this case, it is noteworthy that Sri Lankan Ambassador Mahinda Samarasinghe, who met US Secretary of State Anne J. Blinken and his partner and White House Cabinet Secretary Evan Ryan two weeks ago, briefed them on the country's situation."
      ],
